com.interpss.dc.pv.module

Interface AbstractPVModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IPVModule, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PVModule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPVModuleImpl, PVModuleImpl

    public interface AbstractPVModule
extends NameTag, IPVModule
    A representation of the model object 'Abstract PV Module'. For PVModule extention implementation. You should extend AbstractPVModule and implement the IPVModule interface.

    The following features are supported:

    • Pv Dc Bus
    See Also:
    PVModulePackage.getAbstractPVModule()

      • getPvDcBus

        PVDcBus getPvDcBus()
        Returns the value of the 'Pv Dc Bus' reference. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Pv Module'.

        If the meaning of the 'Dc Bus' reference isn't clear, there really should be more of a description here...
